To use the aws driver, you need to setup the following environment variables:
IAAS=aws
AWS_REGION: the aws region where you want your vms to be. example: REGION=eu-central-1.
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID: your aws access key ID.
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY: your aws secret access key.
AWS_AMI: the amazon machine image you want to create your instances from
AWS_INSTANCE_TYPE: the type of instance you want to create
AWS_PRIVATE_KEY: the path to where you want to save the aws private key
